
<% content_for :before_container do %>
  <div id="welcomeCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
    <!-- Indicators -->
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
      <li data-target="#welcomeCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
      <li data-target="#welcomeCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
      <li data-target="#welcomeCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
      <div class="item active">
        <%= image_tag 'welcome/1.jpg' %>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h1>Only the best recipes you can imagine</h1>
            <p>The recipes here are the finest found on the internet. Checked &amp; scrubbed daily! </p>
            <p><%= link_to 'View recipes', cooking_recipes_path, class:'btn btn-lg btn-primary', role:'button' %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="item">
        <%= image_tag 'welcome/2.jpg' %>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h1>Your own recipes</h1>
            <p>Do you want to submit your own recipes? Click on the button to create an account!</p>
            <p><%= link_to 'Sign up now', register_path, class:'btn btn-lg btn-primary' %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="item">
        <%= image_tag 'welcome/3.jpg' %>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h1>What are you waiting for?</h1>
            <p>Do you want to create a delicious pizza or some amazing Chili Con Carne?</p>
            <p><%= link_to 'Browse recipes', cooking_recipes_path, class:'btn btn-lg btn-primary' %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a class="left carousel-control" href="#welcomeCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#welcomeCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
  </div><!-- /.carousel -->
<% end %>

<!-- Marketing messaging and featurettes
================================================== -->
<!-- Wrap the rest of the page in another container to center all the content. -->

<div class="container marketing">

  <!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->

  <div class="row featurette">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <h2 class="featurette-heading">No more paper or heavy books!</h2>
      <p class="lead">By storing your recipes here, you will never every have to carry all your recipes on paper anymore. No need to lift heavy cook books.</p>
      <h2><span class="text-muted">It'll blow your mind.</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <%= image_tag 'welcome/book.png', class:'featurette-image img-responsive' %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="featurette-divider">

  <div class="row featurette">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <%= image_tag 'welcome/bullhorn.png', class:'featurette-image img-responsive' %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <h2 class="featurette-heading">You will never forget your favorite recipes!</h2>
      <p class="lead">Your recipes are all stored on the great big internet. You will never be able to forget them as you can easily look them up in your account!</p>
      <h2><span class="text-muted">Just bookmark 'em.</span></h2>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="featurette-divider">

  <div class="row featurette">
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <h2 class="featurette-heading">No need to use pen and paper!</h2>
      <p class="lead">Problem with your recipe? Just edit it your recipe and save it, it's updated everywhere with just a click of the mouse!</p>
      <h2><span class="text-muted">Edit your recipe as easy as 1, 2, 3.</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <%= image_tag 'welcome/pen_draft.png', class:'featurette-image img-responsive' %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="featurette-divider">

  <!-- /END THE FEATURETTES -->

  <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <div class="icon"><span aria-hidden="true" data-icon="&#xe01d;"></span></div>
      <h2>Save loads of time</h2>
      <p>You will save loads of time by uploading your recipes and easily look them up. Imagine what you can do with all that time that is saved from now on. Maybe finally start building that car or start a new business? Who knows, everything is possible now!</p>
      <p><%= link_to raw('Sign up today! &raquo;'), register_path, class:'btn btn-default' %></p>
    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <div class="icon"><span aria-hidden="true" data-icon="&#xe00d;"></span></div>
      <h2>Security is our name</h2>
      <p>Your recipes are safe with us. We secure our infrastructure with specially trained gnomes. These <s>little</s> lethal fellows will do anything they can to make sure your recipes are only edited by you and you alone! They even make the developers life miserable by making sure that no data is leaked, sold or thrown on the street.</p>
      <p><%= link_to raw('Sign up today! &raquo;'), register_path, class:'btn btn-default' %></p>
    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <div class="icon"><span aria-hidden="true" data-icon="&#xe01a;"></span></div>
      <h2>It just rocks</h2>
      <p>After using this application, you will walk around with a big smile and know from now on that life is awesome!<br/><br/> Thumbs up, I know you want to!</p>
      <p><%= link_to raw('Login &raquo;'), login_path, class:'btn btn-default' %></p>
    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
  </div><!-- /.row -->

  <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <div class="icon"><span aria-hidden="true" data-icon="&#xe02f;"></span></div>
      <h2>Internationalization</h2>
      <p>This application is available in english and dutch, what ever could you want more?</p>
      <p><%= link_to raw('Sign up today! &raquo;'), register_path, class:'btn btn-default' %></p>
    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <div class="icon"><span aria-hidden="true" data-icon="&#xe006;"></span></div>
      <h2>The power is yours!</h2>
      <p>You alone have the power to create but also delete your own recipes! We have no control whatsoever. They are your recipes and your recipes alone.</p>
      <p><%= link_to raw('See the recipes &raquo;'), cooking_recipes_path, class:'btn btn-default' %></p>
    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
    <div class="col-lg-4">
      <div class="icon"><span aria-hidden="true" data-icon="&#xe026;"></span></div>
      <h2>We love food</h2>
      <p>Our love for food has given us the idea of this awesome application. We know that we're going in the right direction. Want to join us on our quest?</p>
      <p><%= link_to raw('Yes I do! &raquo;'), register_path, class:'btn btn-default' %></p>
    </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
  </div><!-- /.row -->

</div>
